Schedule A Meet-n-Greet
=======================

Hi <%= @application.parent_first_name %>,

I hope this email finds you in good health and spirits! Thank you for taking the time to thoughtfully fill out the enrollment application for our <%= @program.start_date.year %>–<%= (@program.start_date + 1.year).strftime('%y') %> Nature Preschool program. We would love to welcome <%= @application.child_first_name %> and your family to move forward with the next phase of enrollment.

PROGRAM DETAILS
- <%= @program.class_days.presence || 'Days TBD' %>, <%= @program.start_date.strftime('%b %d, %Y') %>–<%= @program.end_date.strftime('%b %d, %Y') %>
<% if @program.formatted_time_range.present? %>- <%= @program.formatted_time_range %>
<% end %><% tuition = @application.effective_tuition_amount || @program.tuition_amount %><% if tuition.present? %>- Tuition: $<%= number_with_precision(tuition, precision: 0, delimiter: ',') %>
<% end %>
<% if @payment_plans.any? %>PAYMENT OPTIONS
<% @application.payment_plan_options.each_with_index do |plan, index| %>- Option <%= index + 1 %>: <%= plan[:name] %> - <%= plan[:description] %>
<% end %><% end %>
A $<%= number_with_precision(@application.effective_enrollment_fee, precision: 0) %> non-refundable enrollment fee is due upon enrollment to reserve your child's spot in the program. Enrollment is for the full school year.

If you'd like to continue the enrollment process, the next step is gathering together for a meet-and-greet at <%= @location&.name || 'Forest Hill Park' %> with the director, Sydney Gary. Spending time together in the space will give us all an opportunity to explore the environment, answer questions, and make sure the nature preschool feels like a good fit for your family.

PLEASE SELECT A DATE:
<% @event.proposed_dates_as_times.each do |date| %>
- <%= date.in_time_zone('Eastern Time (US & Canada)').strftime('%A, %B %d at %I:%M %p') %>
  <%= @base_url %>/meetings/<%= @event.confirmation_token %>/confirm?date=<%= date.to_i %>
<% end %>

Please don't hesitate to reach out with any questions and/or to schedule your visit. We look forward to connecting further!

Warmly,
The Nature Preschool Team
